      <li>Usually less than 1%</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>â€œTwo and twentyâ€
    <ul>
      <li>Classic structure for hedge funds.</li>
      <li>2% of assets under management + 20% of the returns.</li>
      <li>1M with 20% per year = 60k per year</li>
    </ul>
